OL,3,CDoddie Foundation delivers Six Nations
OL,4,Cmatch ball in charity cycle to Dublin
OL,6,FThe riders, including the wife of late
OL,7,Frugby legend and motor neurone disease
OL,8,F(MND) campaigner Doddie Weir, set off
OL,9,Ffrom Edinburgh on Tuesday.
OL,11,FAfter what they said was a gruelling
OL,12,Ffour days, battling severe weather and
OL,13,Fa cancelled ferry, the riders
OL,14,Fsuccessfully delivered the match ball
OL,15,Ffor the Scotland-Ireland rugby tie on
OL,16,Fthe last day of the Six Nations, at
OL,17,Fthe Aviva Stadium in Dublin this
OL,18,Fafternoon (Saturday).
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
