OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1773609119
OL,3,CDoddie Foundation delivers Six Nations
OL,4,Cmatch ball in charity cycle to Dublin
OL,6,FIt was brought onto the pitch ahead of
OL,7,Fkick off by Doddie's wife Kathy Weir
OL,8,Fand Gordon D'Arcy.
OL,10,FThe Doddie's Triple Crown 2026 is the
OL,11,Flatest edition of Rob Wainwright's
OL,12,Fepic annual cycling challenge to raise
OL,13,Fmoney for the My Name'5 Doddie
OL,14,FFoundation and MND research.
OL,16,FThe team covered 750-miles in four
OL,17,Fdays and have raised #1.3m for the
OL,18,Fcharity. It comes off the back of the
OL,19,Fsuccess of Doddie's Grand Tour in
OL,20,F2025, which also raised #1m.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
