PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1773609119
OL,3,CDoddie Foundation delivers Six Nations
OL,4,Cmatch ball in charity cycle to Dublin
OL,6,FEarlier today, the team said, "After
OL,7,Ffour gruelling days, pedalling over
OL,8,F700 miles, this is the emotion moment
OL,9,Four cyclists finally crossed the
OL,10,Ffinish line at Blackrock RFC in Dublin
OL,11,Flast night.
OL,13,F"They've persevered through strong
OL,14,Fheadwinds, torrential downpours and a
OL,15,Fcancelled ferry crossing to name but a
OL,16,Ffew mishaps - all to raise #1.3m and
OL,17,Fcounting for MND research."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
