OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1773609119
OL,3,CDoddie Foundation delivers Six Nations
OL,4,Cmatch ball in charity cycle to Dublin
OL,6,FIt was 55 year old Kathy Weir's 55
OL,7,Ffirst major fundraising challenge, as
OL,8,Fshe joined the herd of 40 teams of
OL,9,Fcyclists as they passed through
OL,10,FMelrose.
OL,12,FScottish Borders star Doddie Weir died
OL,13,Fin November 2022 aged 52 after living
OL,14,Fwith MND for more than six years.
OL,16,FHe founded the My Name'5 Doddie
OL,17,FFoundation in 2017 to fund research
OL,18,Finto MND.JIt was a massive game for
OL,19,Fthe Scotland today as they were still
OL,20,Fin with a chance for their first 6
OL,21,FNations title.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
